  | <p style="text-align:center"><span style="font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:11pt;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none">Free Foto Messenger</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:11pt;font-weight:bold"> Privacy Policy</span></p>
