  | <p> </p>
  | <p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:11pt;text-decoration:underline">Information Disclosed 
  | in Connection with Business Transactions</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:11pt">. Information that we collect from our users, including 
  | PII, is considered to be a business asset. As a result, if we go out 
  | of business or enter bankruptcy or if we are acquired as a result of 
  | a transaction such as a merger, acquisition or asset sale, your PII 
