  | with the transaction.</span></p>
  | <p> </p>
  | <p style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:11pt;text-decoration:underline">Information Disclosed 
  | for Our Protection and the Protection of Others</span><span style="font-family:&#39;Calibri&#39;,&#39;Arial&#39;;font-size:11pt">. It is our policy to protect you from having your 
  | privacy violated through abuse of the legal systems, whether by individuals, 
