  | or law enforcement officials or private parties as we, in our sole discretion, 
  | believe necessary: (i) to satisfy or comply with any applicable law, 
  | regulation or legal process or to respond to lawful requests, including 
  | subpoenas, warrants or court orders; (ii) to protect our property, rights 
  | and safety and the rights, property and safety of third parties or the 
  | public in general; and (iv) to prevent or stop activity we consider 
  | to be illegal or unethical.</span></p>
